name: Bags Super Gloss 9x12 1.25 MIL
description:
Super Gloss Plastic Merchandise bags give you the strength of a reinforced Patch Handle Bag at a much lower price than you would expect to pay.  These bags are strong too, and you’ll still get the gloss and expensive feel that you will love. You will love using these bags in your business. If you would like to have this bag customized with your information and logo and please contact us at 1-800-426-5708 so that we can help you.   
These plastic merchandise bags are made with 20% to 45% recycled material consisting of a combination of post industrial and post consumer resins with a minimum of 5% post consumer recycled (PCR). Made in the U.S.A.
